<div class='panel nonFeedback'>
<h3 title='Overview'><a href='#'></a></h3>

<div class='panelContent nonFeedback'>
<p>This is not a loan, however, it is not just a piece of paper.
Our proof of funds are real accounts with actual cash-backed
deposits.</p>

<ul>
<li>Sometimes Proof of Funds is called 'leased funds' or a 'cash
collateral' account.</li>

<li>We arrange an account in your name or your company's name at
our bank.</li>

<li>The required amount of are deposited into that account.</li>

<li>We remain the sole signatories on the account.</li>

<li>We will open the new account, and the money will never move
from the account.</li>

<li>The account will be in your name for 30 days. Extensions are
available.</li>

<li>We also offer special pricing for those needing Proof of Fund
accounts for length of one or more year.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div class='panel nonFeedback'>
<h3 title='Painless and Easy'><a href='#'></a></h3>

<div class='panelContent nonFeedback'>
<p>These are true cash collateral accounts. The Proof of Funds is
valid for the 30-day period stated and may be extended.</p>

<ul>
<li>NO background check</li>

<li>NO credit report</li>

<li>NO credit scores</li>

<li>NO Business plan</li>

<li>NO Executive summary</li>

<li>NO LTV ratio</li>

<li>NO real estate appraisal</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div class='panel nonFeedback'>
<h3 title='The Perfect Solution'><a href='#'></a></h3>

<div class='panelContent nonFeedback'>
<p>For most balance sheet enhancement needs, a simple Proof of
Funds is the perfect solution.</p>

<p><span class='Highlight'>Our Minimum is Proof of Funds amount
is $1 Million.</span></p>

<p>Set-up time to after a fully executed package is received and
funds are in escrow is 3-5 days. Our funds providing investors
work with top 50 banks. The accounts and banks are recognized
worldwide and pass through any and all compliance and due
diligence tests.</p>

<p>Don't need all the bells and whistles? Just need a simple VOD
and phone/fax confirmation? Either way we have solutions for
you.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class='panel nonFeedback'>
<h3 title='The Upfront Fee Requirement'><a href='#'></a></h3>

<div class='panelContent nonFeedback'>
<p>This is a "funds first" transaction. Because of the
considerable costs involved in providing Proof of Funds we cannot
initiate the process of creating an account for you without
seeing the fee upfront in escrow. We will not accept a delay of
payment until your other transaction closes.</p>

<p>The fee is paid into a third-party escrow account so you are
protected. You remain in control of the funds until you verify
the account and balance exists.</p>

<p>We use a third-party escrow company based in the USA as the
escrow agent. Fees need to be deposited into an escrow account
prior to bank account creation. Once you receive the bank account
letter, you then authorize the release of the fees held in
escrow. This ensures that all parties perform as agreed.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class='panel nonFeedback'>
<h3 title='Step-By-Step Process'><a href='#'></a></h3>

<div class='panelContent nonFeedback'>
<ol>
<li><span class='normal'>Complete the <a href=
'./CISform.php'>Client Information Sheet</a> and submit it. Then
upload the listed documents</span></li>

<li><span class='normal'>A contract is then sent back along with
escrow instructions</span></li>

<li><span class='normal'>Once the fee is wired into escrow we
will have the bank account set-up</span></li>

<li><span class='normal'>Within 48 hours your POF account will be
ready to be verified</span></li>

<li><span class='normal'>The MT-799 or MT-760 is sent according
to your request</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div class='panel nonFeedback'>
<h3 title='Swift (bank-to-bank) Proof of Funds'><a href=
'#'></a></h3>

<div class='panelContent nonFeedback'>
<p><span class='Highlight'>Now we also offer POF accounts with
